"{\"description\":\"Signalling Support Technician role at West Ealing Depot in Wales & Western Region. The role involves providing technical support to the Engineering team and ensuring safe work practices. The successful candidate should be able to work as part of a team, communicate effectively, and hold relevant competencies.\",\"howToApply\":\"To apply, click the 'apply now' button and submit your application before the closing date on 6th December 2023. Late applications will not be accepted. Please note that pre-employment checks, including a drugs and alcohol test, are required for all prospective candidates.\",\"aboutTheRole\":{\"essential\":[\"Able to work as part of a team\",\"Able to communicate effectively verbally and in writing\",\"Hold and retain relevant competencies\",\"Ideally hold or be working towards an NVQ level 1 or 2 in an engineering/leadership subject\",\"Able and willing to drive vehicles as required by business need\"],\"desirable\":[],\"keyAccountabilities\":[\"Carry out work safely and in accordance with the safe systems of work procedures\",\"Adhere to company policies and procedures\",\"Assist in the provision of technical support\",\"Assist in undertaking technical inspections, tests, investigations and analysis of technical data\",\"Assist with the preparation of method statements and/or plans for design or work activities\",\"Provide information and accurately update systems, databases and records\",\"Contribute to your own development and that of others\"]}}"